s=</span><span class=\"s\">\"fa fa-camera-retro fa-4x\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</span> fa-4x\r\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;i</span> <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"fa fa-camera-retro fa-5x\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</span> fa-5x\r\n</code></pre></div>\r\n      <div class=\"alert alert-success\">\r\n        <ul class=\"fa-ul\">\r\n          <li>\r\n            <i class=\"fa fa-exclamation-triangle fa-li fa-lg\"></i>\r\n            If your icons are getting chopped off on top and bottom, make sure you have\r\n            sufficient line-height.\r\n          </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!-- --------- -->\r\n<section id=\"fixed-width\">\r\n  <h4 class=\"page-header\">\r\n    Fixed Width Icons\r\n    <div class=\"pull-right text-default margin-top padding-top-sm hidden-xs\">\r\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome/blob/v4.7.0/less/fixed-width.less\" class=\"text-muted padding-right\">View LESS</a>\r\n	  <span> / </span>\r\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome/blob/v4.7.0/scss/_fixed-width.scss\" class=\"text-muted\">View SASS</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </h4>\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-4\">\r\n      <div class=\"list-group\">\r\n        <a class=\"list-group-item\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home fa-fw\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp; Home</a>\r\n        <a class=\"list-group-item\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-book fa-fw\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp; Library</a>\r\n        <a class=\"list-group-item\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil fa-fw\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp; Applications</a>\r\n        <a class=\"list-group-item\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-cog fa-fw\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp; Settings</a>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-md-9 col-sm-8\">\r\n      <p>\r\n        Use <code>fa-fw</code> to set icons at a fixed width. Great to use when different icon